{
  "stem": "4513.3",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And went to the dance and this black soldier was coming down the steps with this young English lady, his date.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When he got near the front door, we heard the machine gun go off and both of them were killed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the 82nd Airborne.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were riding by with their guns on-- mounted on the jeeps and they strafed the front of the building.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from that point on-- and we had been-- we had been searched before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we couldn't leave the camp with any-- any weapons because we were searched very, very vigorously to be sure we weren't carrying anything, any weapons at all.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here these guys were shooting at our folk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we got-- several of them tried to stop us on the street and we got into a street fight with them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was just awful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Eisenhower finally declared the town off limits because of these fights that we were having with the-- with the 82nd.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- that General Gavin was there, and it was-- they were at the same camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were both occupying the same camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a huge camp up in Leicester.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so Eisenhower declared the town off limits.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said that the black soldiers-- and then he said-- what he changed-- he said-- he'd allow the black soldiers to go downtown to-- to the places where the bars and all were.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the white soldiers would have to go to-- they could go to the suburbs.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
